---
// <Kbd> renders its children inside a styled <kbd>. Inline, for shortcuts.
---

{/* @mdx-label Kbd */}
{/* @mdx-description Inline keyboard key. Use like <Kbd>⌘</Kbd>. */}
{
  /* @mdx-snippet
Press <Kbd>⌘</Kbd> + <Kbd>K</Kbd> to open search.
*/
}
{
  /* @mdx-preview
<p style="font-size:13px;color:#a1a1aa;margin:0">Press
  <kbd style="display:inline-block;padding:.1em .45em;background:#18181b;border:1px solid #3f3f46;border-bottom-width:2px;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px;font-family:monospace;color:#fafafa">⌘</kbd>
  +
  <kbd style="display:inline-block;padding:.1em .45em;background:#18181b;border:1px solid #3f3f46;border-bottom-width:2px;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px;font-family:monospace;color:#fafafa">K</kbd>
  to open search.
</p>
*/
}

<kbd class="kbd"><slot /></kbd>

<style>
  .kbd {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.1em 0.45em;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-hover);
    border-bottom-width: 2px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8em;
    line-height: 1;
    vertical-align: baseline;
  }
</style>
